definition_en: A specific class of stainless steel alloys characterized by an austenitic crystalline structure, known for high corrosion resistance and formability.
definition_ko: 오스테나이트 결정 구조를 특징으로 하며 높은 부식 저항성과 성형성으로 알려진 스테인리스강 합금군.

slots.context_ko: Effects of LWR Coolant Environments on Fatigue Design Curves of Austenitic Stainless Steels
